{"tid":1486810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇你班仆街愚民幾時收皮!","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:14:18.000Z","uid":301661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf0b39368a90ea6c9ca211ebfea857027345bc2","tid":1486810,"uid":301661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"老豆老母深藍分子，親戚一大堆係大陸人<br />\n平時係屋企對住電視屌鳩啲示威者，<br />\n同佢地講點解要上街又唔撚聽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩係識得話：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「搞事就係唔啱，警察好辛苦。」<br />\n「整爛嗮啲公物，塗鴉國旗國徽。」<br />\n「又阻人搵食，和平嘅話我唔會出聲。」<br />\n<br />\n屌鳩佢地無用，平時已經覺得好辛苦。<br />\n仆街今次北上拜祖仲仆街。<br />\n同班親戚朋友食飯先嚟料。<br />\n一開波就話示威者係暴徒，搞搞震。<br />\n聽到我打撚嗮冷震，話搭車唔敢停旺角，<br />\n話示威者打警察，連的士老都拉落嚟打。<br />\n仲要&ldquo;提醒&rdquo;我唔好參與，話會被人拉。<br />\n成班友圍威謂，睇埋嗮啲微信野，<br />\n一齊話示威者嘅不是。<br />\n又話翻上大陸會被人抽後算賬乜乜剩剩。<br />\n驚撚到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n屌到頭嚟咪個句，<br />\n呢班友就係覺得事不關己。<br />\n話唔參與就無事，好人好姐怕咩。<br />\n<br />\n我今日就係到，<br />\n睇你班仆街幾時收皮!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲火&ldquo;辣&rdquo;到埋身嘅時候，咪撚喊。<br />\n我到時一定會同小鳳姐一齊，<br />\n笑到你地仆街!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打得呢篇野，<br />\n預咗被人屌到我個背景仆街。<br />\n但我真係忍唔撚住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">If we burn, you burn with us!</span>"},{"pid":"aa10419baafc13dfa3bcb0da2aa77dd7801d2b36","tid":1486810,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDmhmk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDmhmk5.jpg&h=d0ecb5b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ce4e08f7c0be4fb219bfb857ac6b4fad6522f76","tid":1486810,"uid":301661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c363a540ced007911376d0e22d468dec6c70e934","tid":1486810,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"同你老豆老母講大灣區未來發展潛力高，叫佢地賣咗香港層樓返去投資"},{"pid":"070180f6d15340781a5a6dfb249e4a8fb192dcfd","tid":1486810,"uid":200136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c363a540ced007911376d0e22d468dec6c70e934","tid":1486810,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"同你老豆老母講大灣區未來發展潛力高，叫佢地賣咗香港層樓返去投資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"到時危樓唔好救"},{"pid":"994cb83c295e550825cf2db3c4d4823a4df3eaf0","tid":1486810,"uid":301661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"以後佢地中撚咗毒奶粉,垃圾焚化場,貪污...<br />\n遇到任何不公平對待嘅時候，<br />\n我睇你班愚民去邊到投訴。<br />\n<br />\n被行李碌到腳，係你自己揀。<br />\n成街屎尿垃圾，係你自己揀。<br />\n變成D級公民，係你自己揀。<br />\n天災每人三毫子，係你自己揀。<br />\n銀行存款變嗮股份，係你自己揀。<br />\n<br />\n想報警？被黑社會打到仆街。<br />\n想遊行？隔日就人間蒸發。<br />\n<br />\n講多無謂，呢班仆街係要中咗先識喊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}